snippet.title: LSC Colloquium: Lanier Holt "Where are we going? Examining the Media’s Role in Race Perception"
snippet.description: Dr. Lanier Holt, Assistant Professor in the School of Communications at The Ohio State University, joins LSC virtually to discuss the status of Black-White relations today, the media’s role in it, why Whites have a negative opinion of Blacks, and what can be done to both identify and possibly negate negative racial opinions borne from media messages.
